Jos &mdash; Governor Simon Lalong of Plateau State has said the main reason his administration organized the Jos Carnival was to consolidate on permanent peace in the state and use the exhibitions during the carnival to bring back investors who fled following the crisis that bedeviled the state.Lalong stated this in a speech at the closing ceremony of the maiden edition of the Jos Carnival, reiterating that the state was now a safe zone for investors to carry on their businesses without fear.The maiden Jos Carnival kicked off on April 12 with a fiesta for Plateau children. The carnival is intended to be an annual affair as applicable in a number of other states across the country.